This file is a marker for auto-determining language server's typst root.
In my nvim setup I use:

    vim.lsp.config('tinymist', {
        offset_encoding = 'utf-32', -- tinymist seems to be bugged
        root_dir = function(bufnr, on_dir)
            local auto_root = vim.fs.root(bufnr, '.typst_project')
            if auto_root ~= nil then
                on_dir(auto_root)
            else
                on_dir(vim.fs.dirname(vim.api.nvim_buf_get_name(bufnr)))
            end
        end
    })

You can set root to / or this directory.
